wayfindings.text: Enterprise is at both the Lindbergh and Humphrey terminals of the MSP Airport.
If flying into Lindbergh, take the tram from baggage claim to the rental car facility. Take the elevator to Level 3.
If flying into Humphrey, take the skyway across the street.  From there, take the elevator down to Level 1. Enterprise will be outside the elevator.
Self-service kiosks at this location makes your rental transaction quick and easy.
Or proceed to the Enterprise counter to obtain your rental agreement and keys.
